research_municipality_step.notes: The elected officials were identified from the Texas Municipal League City Officials Directory and the City of Grey Forest's official website. The results of the May 4, 2024, general election were used to confirm the current Mayor and Council Members for Places 2 and 4. While Grey Forest is a General Law Type A city, typically having a Mayor and five Aldermen (Council Members), specific 'Place' designations were not consistently available for all council members in the search results. Aurelia Scharnhorst, previously listed as a council member, was not re-elected in the May 2024 election for Place 4.
